Class GraphAdapter

java.lang.Object
fr.u_paris.gla.project.dijkstra.GraphAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
TransportGraph
public class GraphAdapter extends Object implements TransportGraph
Adapter class to convert a Graph from the IDFM project to a TransportGraph for Dijkstra's algorithm.
